ACTIVITY 1

Reference of YOUTUBE:
1.	S1: New user account in Gmail/YouTube(sign-up)

YouTube:

•	Publisher : User Registration Service/Account Verification Service
•	Subscriber : Welcome Notification service or notification service

Gmail:
•	Publisher : User Registration Service/Email Validation Service/Password Service/Account Initialization Service
•	Subscriber : Welcome Email Service or Notification Service

2.	S2 : The user logs in to YT using the account(sign_in)
YouTube:
•	Publisher : Authentication Service/User Profile Service/Analytics Service
•	Subscriber : User Activity Service/Logging Service/Security Service/Error Handling Service

3.	S3 : Create a subscription service in YT
YouTube:
•	Publisher : Recommendation Service/Subscription Management Service/Billing Service
•	Subscriber : notification services/list services

4.	S4 : User :: Create a channel
YouTube:
•	Publisher : Channel Creation Service/Channel Verification Service/Language Service/ Media Integration Service
•	Subscriber : Email Notification Service/Channel Updated Service



5.	S5 :: user --> channel --> uploads a video
YouTube:
•	Publisher : Video Upload Service/Content Management Service/Video Processing Service/ Service
•	Subscriber : Notification Service/Transcript Generation Service/Thumbnail Service/Video Storage Service/Video Service
